videos.description: Lakers coach Luke Walton says in a postgame news conference that the reason he pulled Lonzo Ball was because his dad, LaVar, was talking trash. Walton quickly adds "I'm just kidding" and explains Lonzo's fatigue.
videos.headline: Walton jokes that LaVar is reason he pulled Lonzo
